doc.after: Boeing developed military jets such as the B 47 Stratojet and B 52 Stratofortress bombers in the late 1940s and into the 1950s During the early 1950s Boeing used company funds to develop the 367 80 jet airliner demonstrator that led to the KC 135 Stratotanker and Boeing 707 jetliner
